{"data":[{"date":"14:52 24/07","title":"Maradona t\u1eebng qua \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Icardi","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/maradona-tung-qua-dem-voi-vo-tien-dao-icardi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin \u1edf Argentina kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 'C\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng' t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian m\u1eb7n n\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Icardi.</h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Mirtha Legrand b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh, ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Maradona. Theo \u0111\u00f3, MC 91 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft b\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam \u0111am m\u00ea gi\u1eefa huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Icardi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 n\u0103m 2006, Wanda Nara t\u1eebng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2006 khi c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Maradona. C\u00f4 n\u00e0y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan h\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Mirtha Legrand b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00f3i l\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec7n c\u0169 trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \"\u0110\u00eam c\u1ee7a Mirtha\" t\u1ea1i Argentina v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maradona t\u1eebng qua \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maradona t\u1eebng qua \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/cc2-2937-1532399591.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Maradona t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian c\u1eb7p k\u00e8 Wanda Nara. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e0 \u1edf c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u1edf Mar de Plata v\u00e0 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n ch\u1ee9ng khi nghe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e2m thanh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00eam \u0111am m\u00ea c\u1ee7a Maradona. \"T\u00f4i \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa \u0103n tr\u01b0a \u1edf Mar del Plata, \u1edf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Costa Galana \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00ean s\u00f3ng, c\u00f4 \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n t\u00f4i v\u00e0 n\u00f3i t\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng m\u1eddi c\u00f4 \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn bu\u1ed5i bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n. T\u00f4i h\u1ecfi l\u1ea1i c\u00f4 \u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng c\u00f4 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 v\u1edbi Maradona \u00e0. H\u1ecd d\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i ng\u1ee7 y\u00ean trong \u0111\u00eam\", Mirtha Legrand b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ee7 t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n. T\u00f4i xin n\u00f3i s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc\", ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u1ea7n quan h\u1ec7 t\u00ecnh d\u1ee5c \"kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf\" c\u1ee7a Maradona v\u00e0 Wanda Nara.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMirtha Legrand c\u00f2n k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecnh th\u1ea5y Wanda Nara xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi trang ph\u1ee5c l\u00f3t khi \u0111ang n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n trong c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Maradona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWanda Nara \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i s\u00e1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u1ed3n \u00e0o v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i t\u00ecnh tay ba c\u00f9ng Maxi Lopez v\u00e0 Icardi - hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4570","checkdouble":"191914"},{"date":"14:57 24/07","title":"B\u1ed3 hoa h\u1eadu g\u1eedi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ozil","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/bo-hoa-hau-gui-thong-diep-yeu-thuong-den-tien-ve-ozil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2> Amine Gulse, hoa h\u1eadu Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 2014 lu\u00f4n s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng Ozil trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n, Mesut Ozil g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, c\u00f9ng 3 b\u1ee9c th\u01b0 d\u00e0i n\u00f3i r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 b\u1ee9c x\u00fac trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018. Ozil th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \"v\u1eadt t\u1ebf th\u1ea7n\" cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 l\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00f9a r\u00ecu d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Ozil l\u00e0 Amine Gulse \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean b\u1ea1n trai. Hoa h\u1eadu Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 2014 \u0111\u0103ng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: \"Lu\u00f4n b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 anh, anh y\u00eau\".\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/2-1532413736006592055948.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Ozil m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng khai h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i t\u00ecnh tay ba. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Ozil c\u00f3 th\u1eddi chia tay Gulse \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 v\u1edbi n\u1eef ca s\u0129 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Mandy Capristo. M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a Ozil ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGulse, b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Ozil, sinh n\u0103m 1994. C\u00f4 sinh ra \u1edf Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, m\u1eb9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iraq. Gulse n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef9 khi \u0111\u0103ng quang Hoa h\u1eadu n\u0103m 2014 v\u00e0 tham gia m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng Ozil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00ednh h\u00f4n v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i, song ch\u01b0a \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 c\u01b0\u1edbi.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4569","checkdouble":"191915"},{"date":"15:02 24/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e2m ch\u1ebft sau cu\u1ed9c \u1ea9u \u0111\u1ea3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/thu-mon-nguoi-argentina-bi-dam-chet-sau-cuoc-au-da-voi-dong-nghiep.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4568","checkdouble":"191916"},{"date":"16:28 24/07","title":"CLB tham d\u1ef1 Serie A 2018/19 s\u1edbm b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m do b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/24/clb-tham-du-serie-a-201819-som-bi-tru-5-diem-do-ban-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Serie A c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a kh\u1edfi tranh nh\u01b0ng CLB Parma \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9m 19 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1edbi 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m do b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italy \u0111\u01b0a tin, T\u00f2a \u00e1n li\u00ean bang Italy (TNF) v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh cho Parma b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec3m (5) \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/2019. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 do h\u00e0nh vi b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Emanuele Calaio. V\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Calaio c\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 t\u1edbi 2 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y, TNF \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec1u tra nh\u1eefng tin nh\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Calaio g\u1eedi cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB Spezia v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tin nh\u1eafn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Parma b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i Serie A 201819 do b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB Parma b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i Serie A 201819 do b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/parma1_geeq.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CLB Parma s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 \u00e2m 5.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCalaio t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Spezia tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, TNF k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn anh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafn cho 2 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 l\u00e0 Filippo De Col v\u00e0 Claudio Terzi n\u1ed9i dung nh\u1eb1m khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y &quot;thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu t\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh h\u01a1n&quot;. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 2 n\u0103m, Calaio c\u00f2n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 20 ngh\u00ecn euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Parma, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t tr\u1eeb 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho hay h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ph\u00e1n quy\u1ebft k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1ng \u00e1n t\u1edbi c\u00f9ng. Tuy v\u1eady, Parma n\u00ean c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y may m\u1eafn khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, TNF cho hay: &quot;T\u00f2a \u00e1n li\u00ean bang Italy \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n b\u1edfi Mario Antonio Scino, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t tr\u1eeb 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi CLB Parma \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/2019, c\u00f9ng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Emanuele Calaio&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hay c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Italy b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t v\u00ec d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n l\u1ea1. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, scandal Calciopoli t\u1eebng l\u00e0m rung chuy\u1ec3n n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Juventus b\u1ecb gi\u00e1ng xu\u1ed1ng Serie B. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n l\u00e0 scandal Scommessopoli khi\u1ebfn HLV Conte su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i h\u1ea7u t\u00f2a.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4567","checkdouble":"191923"},{"date":"12:45 24/07","title":"B\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018: Khi ph\u00e9p vua c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thua l\u1ec7 l\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh song cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>UAE, Palestine \u0111\u1ea9y ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 x\u1eed</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ebf b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m 24 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 6 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eb1m trong m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 c\u00f9ng Hong Kong, L\u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0i Loan.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1i quy t\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3ng F v\u1edbi 3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, Arab Saudi v\u00e0 Iran.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 Khi ph\u00e9p vua c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thua l\u1ec7 l\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 Khi ph\u00e9p vua c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thua l\u1ec7 l\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Boc-tham-ASIAD-2018-Khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ch\u1ea7n ch\u1eeb trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n b\u1ed5 sung 3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n UAE, Palestine v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Olympic \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, L\u0110B\u0110 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (AFC) v\u00e0 \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA) \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee3i \u00fd hai ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD, ho\u1eb7c s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n cho 3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u00e0 UAE, Palestine v\u00e0 \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xem ch\u1eebng Indonesia \u0111ang h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n hai, b\u1edfi nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp theo. V\u00ec v\u1eady, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u01b0a 3 \u0111\u1ed9i UAE, \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&nbsp;Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch&nbsp;\u1ee6y ban Olympic Indonesia&nbsp;(INASGOC) Erick Thohir kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i sau n\u00e0y chia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n t\u1eeb b\u1ea3ng A \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea3ng F. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, r\u1ea5t r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i&rdquo;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 nh\u00ec 2 b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u1ee6y ban Olympic Indonesia tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Khi ph\u00e9p vua c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thua l\u1ec7 l\u00e0ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c BTC n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 \u0111ang t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;c\u00e2u gi\u1edd&rdquo; vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam \u1edf ASIAD 2018 cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p trong th\u1ec3 thao n\u00f3i chung v\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00f3i ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, h\u00f4m qua (23/7), Indonesia ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n chia 27 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n thu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c L\u0110B\u0110 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean ch\u00e2u \u00c1 d\u1ef1 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam \u1edf \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i n\u0103m nay. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd chia l\u00e0m 8 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u (5 b\u1ea3ng 3 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 3 b\u1ea3ng 4 \u0111\u1ed9i). \u0110\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. Tuy nhi\u00ean cho t\u1edbi ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t, bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m s\u1edbm s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1t ru\u1ed9t nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda BTC n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia l\u1ea1i t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;c\u00e2u gi\u1edd&rdquo;, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Asiad 2018\" title=\"Asiad 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-se-thi-dau-tuong-tu-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>N\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 v\u1eabn ch\u1ea7n ch\u1eeb trong vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec7n Indonesia nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u0169ng c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 trong vi\u1ec7c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, t\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd AFC Datuk Windsor John Paul c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Indonesia. &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0103n b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda nh\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a OCA v\u00e0 INASGOC&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, Indonesia \u0111ang bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 khi ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5 trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc V\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 trong th\u1ec3 thao.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb t\u1ea1i SEA Games 26 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Indonesia n\u0103m 2015, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfng x\u1ea5u trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 ASIAD, vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Indonesia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 th\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha-168-191682.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/8/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha-168-191682.html\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp t\u1edbi 7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park-168-191683.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park-168-191683.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\n12 &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a HLV Park...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4566","checkdouble":"191908"},{"date":"15:00 24/07","title":"Sao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/10/van-quyet-khong-ngai-boc-tham-lai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec7n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/2/Van-Quyet-khong-ngai-boc-tham-lai-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 nhau</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh song cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho hay: \u201cTh\u1eadt ra t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo l\u1eafng hay b\u1ea5t an khi BTC c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD 2018. V\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh h\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. V\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o \u1edf ASIAD th\u00ec to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 100%, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 200% s\u1ee9c trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn m\u1ed9t m\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. S\u1edf d\u0129 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t b\u1edfi anh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 su\u1ea5t cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 n\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng sau.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-168-191908.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-168-191908.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018: Khi ph\u00e9p vua c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thua l\u1ec7 l\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh song cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4565","checkdouble":"191909"},{"date":"14:56 24/07","title":"L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/24/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia m\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia).</h2><h2>\u1ea4n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Trong l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m hy h\u1eefu khi b\u1ecf qu\u00ean Palestine v\u00e0 UAE. V\u00ec v\u1eady, l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Le boc tham lai bong da nam ASIAD 2018 dien ra vao ngay 25/7.\" title=\"L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 25/7.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 25/7 t\u1ea1i&nbsp;tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia).</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia). Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n v\u00e0o v\u00e0o 14h00 ng\u00e0y 25/7.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>M\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 26 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1, chia th\u00e0nh 6 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng A, C, D, F s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u00f2n b\u1ea3ng B v\u00e0 E s\u1ebd c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i. Hai b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10/8, thay v\u00ec 14/8 nh\u01b0 l\u1ecbch ban b\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng th\u1eafc m\u1eafc<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>D\u00f9 v\u1eady, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra ho\u00e0i nghi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i. Ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 t\u1edd Bolabob c\u1ee7a Indonesia cho bi\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t chia hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n, thay v\u00ec b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang dau cua DT Olympic Viet Nam tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/bang-asiad.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3ng th\u00f4ng t\u1ea5n Xinhua th\u00ec cho bi\u1ebft Indonesia d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B, E c\u1ee7a k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f2n L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (KFA) c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ngo\u00e0i Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia v\u00e0 Bahrain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eefa, l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10 ho\u1eb7c 12/8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e3n l\u1ea7n hai (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23/7) n\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd d\u1eddi sang ng\u00e0y 27/7.\r\n<h2><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-168-191908.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018: Khi ph\u00e9p vua c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thua l\u1ec7 l\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/so-vao-bang-kho-indonesia-hoan-le-boc-tham-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-292-191883.html\">S\u1ee3 v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f3, Indonesia ho\u00e3n l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon-292-191799.html\">Nh\u1eefng ai trong \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018-292-191795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-chau-a-afc-noi-gi-ve-kha-nang-boc-tham-lai-asiad-168-191785.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4564","checkdouble":"191911"},{"date":"12:45 24/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 24/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 24/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2407 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2407 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2407-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 Real g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Navas kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Navas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 ngay c\u1ea3 khi Courtois c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, ph\u00eda Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a M.U, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Marcelo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcelo Ronaldo\" title=\"Marcelo Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/13/Them-mot-ngoi-sao-khang-dinh-Cristiano-Ronaldo-la-so-1-the-gioi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Marcelo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Ronaldo \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge, hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Petr Cech l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 Real mua Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Marca, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Thibaut Courtois cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Petr Cech t\u1eeb Arsenal. The Blues ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 36 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Nabil Fekir&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon. Liverpool v\u1eeba tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i, Lyon \u0111\u00f2i 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Jose Mourinho mu\u1ed1n mua Kroos ho\u1eb7c Varane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hang phong ngu Real Madrid de lai noi lo khi Varane dinh chan thuong.\" title=\"H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i lo khi Varane d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/7/tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-36-mourinho-ru-re-tro-cu-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU mua Varane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo Don Balon, HLV Jose Mourinho mu\u1ed1n mua Toni Kroos ho\u1eb7c Raphael Varane t\u1eeb Real Madrid, M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Kroos v\u00e0 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Varane.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Gareth Bale quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Julen Lopetegui tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4563","checkdouble":"191907"},{"date":"16:52 24/07","title":"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \"gi\u00e1 m\u1ec1m\" m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-muc-tieu-gia-mem-ma-real-madrid-co-the-chieu-mo-thay-vi-eden-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi chia tay Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00ean t\u1edbi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn 'gi\u00e1 m\u1ec1m' h\u01a1n cho Real.</h2><h2>3. Anthony Martial</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed3i cho Real trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho song Martial v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp ghi nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 31 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 131 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Martial song v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf Wayne Rooney, Martial l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League, n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 Ander Herrera c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng anh th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/3-muc-tieu-ma-Real-Madrid-co-the-chieu-mo-thay-vi-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Martial s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn '\u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ec1n' v\u1edbi CLB Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Martial v\u1edbi M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau tuy nhi\u00ean hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Do v\u1eady \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 Real nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e9p gi\u00e1 Man United.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN th\u00ec c\u1ea3 Chelsea, Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Martial nh\u01b0ng HLV Mourinho ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n anh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Real Madrid. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Martial m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Sadio Mane</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Mohamed Salah, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sadio Mane c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, Mane lu\u00f4n cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng The Kop/\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 20 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Liverpool tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1edd t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Mane lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Real ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HLV Zidane \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac khi c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean Mane v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u00edch h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Real. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Mane ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 d\u01b0\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span> th\u00edch h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah va Mane\" title=\"Salah va Mane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/liverpool-toi-my-du-dau-tam-tau-ke-o-nguoi-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 Mane r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi Real</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>1. Ivan Perisic</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Croatia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. V\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, Perisic lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c th\u1eeba. Trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c x\u00e9 toang h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic la tru cot cua Inter\" title=\"Ivan Perisic la tru cot cua Inter\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Ivan-Perisic-la-tru-cot-cua-Inter.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ivan Perisic \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i\u00a0Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, m\u1ed7i khi x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp trung l\u1ed9, Perisic th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00e1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi anh lu\u00f4n l\u00f9i s\u00e2u tranh ch\u1ea5p khu gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Perisic ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t 'm\u00f3n h\u1eddi' cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y thay v\u00ec c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Eden Hazard t\u1eeb Chelsea.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407-180-191907.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407-180-191907.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 24/07</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 24/07.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Marca, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Mauro Icardi \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-ra-di-ai-se-mang-ve-50-ban-thang-moi-mua-cho-real-187-191545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-he-2018-hua-hen-se-no-bom-tan-sau-CR7-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-ra-di-ai-se-mang-ve-50-ban-thang-moi-mua-cho-real-187-191545.html\">Ronaldo ra \u0111i: Ai s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a cho Real?</span><br>\r\nChia tay Cristiano Ronaldo, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ef1 ph\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e2u ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4562","checkdouble":"191925"},{"date":"17:08 24/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t San Jose Earthquakes","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhung-van-de-cua-mu-sau-tran-hoa-nhat-san-jose-earthquakes.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>San Jose Earthquakes hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng khu v\u1ef1c mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i MLS. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Man United s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn l\u1eafm m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/170116-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man United kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. Man United t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 571 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 85%. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mourinho tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadm, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Martial, Sanchez v\u00e0 Chong tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian khi nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, qu\u00e3ng chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhanh nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd, Mourinho v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Valencia \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man United. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc n\u00e0y, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1i t\u0103m l\u00e0 Matteo Darmian. N\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 Fosu-Mensah, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc San Jose Earthquakes</span> ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nan gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Pogba th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t khi thi\u1ebfu Lukaku\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba va Lukaku\" title=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Nhan-dinh-co-hoi-MU-vo-dich-giai-Ngoai-hang-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Lukaku</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Man United trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Ngo\u00e0i Lukaku, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tay s\u0103n b\u00e0n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. V\u1eady n\u00ean m\u1ed7i khi thi\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao cao to ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u1ea1i b\u1ebf t\u1eafc t\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng gi\u00fap MU thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n sau khi gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn M\u1ef9. V\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1m \u1ed5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i MLS. Nh\u01b0ng ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, Sanchez h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 HLV Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee9ng ra \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n. C\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i Lukaku, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u01a1 h\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anthony Martial\" title=\"Anthony Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Wayne-Rooney-khuyen-MU-giu-chan-Martial-bang-moi-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a khi \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Martial nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec Man United. \u0110\u1ea7u \u00f3c c\u1ee7a Martial \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c sau khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford. V\u00e0 Mourinho c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Martial \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh khi quay l\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y th\u00ec kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Martial, Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Martial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Martial l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c n\u00ean l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Man United. B\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Sanchez kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Martial c\u0169ng g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p x\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-arturo-vidal-sap-ky-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-191920.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-247-187-191902.html\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 24/7: M.U ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua trung v\u1ec7 Maguire</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4561","checkdouble":"191926"},{"date":"17:48 24/07","title":"Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00ean 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/7/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-trung-ve-nguoi-italia-len-45-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Chelsea-mua-Daniele-Rugani-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang-tu-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Juventus 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Rugani cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Rugani ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 20 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Serie A, anh g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho Rugani kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Milan, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Juventus. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb, Chelsea sau \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00ean 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 h\u1ecfi mua Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-cong-bo-tan-binh-thu-2-tri-gia-36-trieu-bang-172-191548.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. The Blues \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rugani nhieu kha nang se tro thanh tan binh dau tien cua Arsenal o He 2018\" title=\"Rugani nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/chelsea-sap-cong-bo-tan-binh-thu-2-tri-gia-36-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Rugani l\u00ean 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 David Luiz v\u00e0 Gary Cahill. The Blues d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Rugani n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 HLV Sarri: \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, Sarri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV t\u1ed1t. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Rugani v\u1edbi Juventus v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn 3 n\u0103m, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Juventus c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng hay kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4560","checkdouble":"191927"},{"date":"17:29 24/07","title":"Scholes l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/scholes-chi-trich-mourinho-vi-da-giao-huu-qua-kem.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Scholes r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Man United v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho sau 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf M\u1ef9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>MU \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch v\u1edbi 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u00edt h\u01a1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Man City t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. V\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 b\u1eb1ng hai m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Club America v\u00e0 San Jose Earthquakes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap cho NHM c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb san l\u1ea5p. Nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Mourinho v\u1eabn mong mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Scholes ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho v\u00ec qu\u00e1 coi tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Scholes ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho v\u00ec qu\u00e1 coi tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/scholes-chi-trich-mourinho-vi-da-giao-huu-qua-kem.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Scholes ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho v\u00ec qu\u00e1 coi tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Paul Scholes v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong th\u1eddi gian qua.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cMourinho c\u00f3 l\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man United thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mong mu\u1ed1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1o ra k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t thay v\u00ec l\u00e0m cho b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Mourinho h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng n\u0103m c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Pep Guardiola l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a Man United, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t gh\u00e9t nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Mourinho l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 d\u1ef1a theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1eafng tay th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi MU</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Man United \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o. V\u00e0 Scholes tin r\u1eb1ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cN\u0103m ngo\u00e1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Man United kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Sevilla, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 \u1edf Champions League. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft FA Cup nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed7i n\u0103m tr\u1eafng tay \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi Man United\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-mu-sau-tran-hoa-nhat-san-jose-earthquakes-172-191926.html\">Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t San Jose Earthquakes</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-cau-thu-vo-danh-172-191899.html\">MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 danh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4559","checkdouble":"191929"},{"date":"17:19 24/07","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-willian-toi-barca.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Willian t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Pedro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Conte th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Willian v\u00e0 Pedro \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 17 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 20 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-Willian-toi-Barca--hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pedro h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i n\u1ebfu Willian ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Willian l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Pedro. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Barca ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 4 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Napoli, HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Willian s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u01a1n Pedro \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca, nghi\u1ec5m nhi\u00ean Pedro s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Camp Nou, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui nh\u1ea5t, b\u1edfi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden Hazard \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos, anh c\u0169ng b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1ebd gi\u1eef Hazard n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Eden Hazard</span>, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu Willian c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Hazard s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid. HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t Willian \u00f4ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c gi\u1eef Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Philippe Coutinho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Philippe Coutinho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Willian nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho se rat vui neu Willian toi Barca\" title=\"Coutinho s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/coutinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Coutinho s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Coutinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng khi\u1ebfn Coutinho h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Barca 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 50, 53 v\u00e0 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCoutinho ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui nh\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu Barca \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Willian. Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau 30 l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n \u1edf World Cup 2018.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 am hi\u1ec3u gi\u1eefa Coutinho v\u00e0 Willian s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Barca c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Coutinho c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Willian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ousmane Dembele c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u1ec9 ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Dembele th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele co the roi Camp Nou neu Barca mua Willian\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/dem.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Willian, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ousmane Dembele ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, Willian ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, Willian s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Messi v\u00e0 Suarez l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Barca ngay \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Wilfried Zaha</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian, HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n duy nh\u1ea5t Pedro l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilfried Zaha co co hoi khoac ao Chelsea neu Willian ra di\" title=\"Wilfried Zaha c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u1ebfu Willian ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/zaha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilfried Zaha c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u1ebfu Willian ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAnthony Martial l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song Mourinho \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i. M.U d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eafn ch\u1eb7t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martial t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ESPN v\u00e0 Mirror, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Wilfried Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nZaha \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Palace, anh \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edbi Stamford Bridge, Zaha s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 MU</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Willian, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Chelsea gi\u00fap \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988. Mourinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho rat muon tai hop voi Willian o MU\" title=\"Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/mou.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf Old Trafford, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. Daily Mail v\u00e0 Goal \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Willian c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 Mourinho tan th\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Chelsea s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca thay v\u00ec M.U, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai l\u1ea7m khi b\u00e1n Matic cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4558","checkdouble":"191930"}]}